    "Although open-access datasets have improved reproducibility, several studies still rely on proprietary or local data, which limits cross-country comparisons.",
    "For instance, national banking datasets or small cryptocurrency samples may not generalize to other contexts.",
    "Future research could benefit from standardized financial data repositories and more transparent sharing of code and parameters [20].",
